// Baked reference-image data for the mountain splash scene.
//
// This is NOT procedurally generated — it's a real 24-bit RGB render of
// the reference mountain artwork, cropped down to ONLY the sky+ridge
// content (420x43, row-major, base64-encoded, decoded at runtime with
// Node's built-in Buffer — no extra dependency). The original capture
// included a decorative top/bottom border stripe (redundant with the
// dotted rule ui.js already draws) and a blurry baked-in mascot silhouette
// at the bottom-left; both were cropped out here so mountainScene() can
// draw its own crisp mascot and its own stars on top of pure terrain.
export const MOUNTAIN_GRID_W = 420;
export const MOUNTAIN_GRID_H = 43;
export const MOUNTAIN_GRID_B64 = '';
